text: KHDL (99.5 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Americus, Kansas. The station is owned by Robert Young, and airs a classic country/red dirt format. The station was assigned the KHDL call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on June 20, 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for KHDL * HDL Category:Radio stations established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in Kansas Category:Classic country radio stations in the United States Category:Lyon County, Kansas
